---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us - ToyVault" description="Learn about ToyVault's mission to bring joy through quality toys">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="container about-content">
    <h1>About ToyVault</h1>
    
    <p>Welcome to ToyVault, your premier destination for quality toys and games that bring joy to children and families.</p>
    
    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>Founded in 2026, ToyVault was born from a passion for childhood wonder and the belief that play is essential to development. We carefully curate our collection to include only the best toys that inspire creativity, learning, and fun.</p>
    
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>To provide families with access to high-quality, safe, and engaging toys that create lasting memories and support child development.</p>
    
    <h2>Why Choose ToyVault?</h2>
    <ul style="margin-left: var(--space-lg);">
      <li>Carefully curated selection of 2000+ premium toys</li>
      <li>Quality guaranteed - we test every product</li>
      <li>Fast and reliable delivery across India</li>
      <li>Excellent customer service</li>
      <li>Competitive pricing</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Have questions? We'd love to hear from you! Visit our <a href="/contact">contact page</a> or reach us at hello@toyvault.com</p>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>